entry.title: Special Weather Statement issued April 23 at 1:13AM EDT by NWS Mount Holly NJ
entry.summary:
The combination of low relative humidity values between 20 and 30 percent, southerly winds around 10-15 mph, gusting between 15 to 20 mph, and drying fuels will increase the potential for the spread of fires this afternoon.
